text: "Lips of an Angel" is a song recorded by American country music artist Jack Ingram. ==Music video== The music video was directed by Shaun Silva and premiered in January 11, 2007. The video debuted at number 20 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of January 25, 2007. The music video reached number 1 on CMT's Top Twenty Countdown for the week of March 15, 2007. ==References== Category:2006 songs Category:Jack Ingram songs Category:Music videos directed by Shaun Silva
